title: AOC: 'Brown Women Can't Be President' | Guest: Marco Rubio
description: We debut a new series today: MAKE MY PROFESSOR FAMOUS. Wait until you see the first professor we have attempting to indoctrinate students. Also, Rep. AOC said a lot of dumb stuff to GQ.
